```
docs: Document lock ordering hierarchy in BridgeServer and WebSocketMiddleware

Prevents future changes from introducing deadlocks by documenting
the implicit ordering: cleanup_mutex_ > last_sent_mutex_ > stats_mutex_
(BridgeServer) and state_mutex_ > clients_mutex_ > queue_mutex_
(WebSocketMiddleware).
```

